title: Johnson welcomes 'phenomenal' response to depression admission
text:
Johnson welcomes 'phenomenal' response to depression admission   00:48 
Actor Dwayne ''The Rock'' Johnson, one of Hollywood's top paid stars, said on Wednesday (April 11) he'd had a 'phenomenal' response after opening up about his past struggle with depression. Rough cut (no reporter narration)
